data.description: Welcome Home to your 3bd/2ba home in the Western Alamance school district. This one level home boasts new paint througout home. Kitchen w/ stainless steel appliances.  Master bedroom w/ ensuite and new carpet.  The backyard is perfect for all of your family gatherings with a fenced yard, attached and detached stoage and  nestled in a cul-da-sac. Do not miss out on your chance to view this gem. Schedule your private tour before it's too late.
